Enum KeyPurposeId

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<KeyPurposeId>
      • org.security.crypt.x509.types.KeyPurposeId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<KeyPurposeId>

    public enum KeyPurposeId
extends java.lang.Enum<KeyPurposeId>
    Represents the KeyPurposeId type described in section 4.2.1.13 of RFC 2459, which is used to indicate extended key usage.
    Author:
    shivam
